GitHub Repository: agentic-flow

Agentic reasoning and multi-agent systems

Installation & Setup Commands:
1. import { ReflexionMemory, SkillLibrary, CausalMemoryGraph } from 'agentic-flow/agentdb';
2. import { ModelRouter } from 'agentic-flow/router';
3. import * as reasoningbank from 'agentic-flow/reasoningbank';
4. import { AgentBooster } from 'agentic-flow/agent-booster';
5. import { QuicTransport } from 'agentic-flow/transport/quic';
6. import { SwarmLearningOptimizer, autoSelectSwarmConfig } from 'agentic-flow/hooks/swarm-learning-optimizer';
7. helm install agentic-jujutsu agentic-jujutsu/agentic-jujutsu-controller \
8. import { BillingSystem } from 'agentic-flow/billing';
9. const billing = new BillingSystem({ enableMetering: true });
10. npm install agentic-jujutsu
11. import { JJOperation, QuantumSigning } from 'agentic-jujutsu';
12. const op = new JJOperation({
13. const signer = new QuantumSigning();
14. import { DataSharingControls } from 'agentic-flow/consent';
15. const controls = new DataSharingControls();
16. import { LeanAgenticIntegration } from 'agentic-flow/verification';
17. const integration = new LeanAgenticIntegration();
18. # Global installation
19. npm install -g agentic-flow
20. # Or use directly with npx (no installation)

Repository: https://github.com/ruvnet/agentic-flow
